headline: Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory Appoints Jack Abraham and Terri Keogh to Board of Trustees
summary: The Cold Spring Harbor Laboratory (CSHL) Board of Trustees has elected Jack Abraham to the private not-for-profit institution's governing body. Abraham is the founder, CEO, and managing partner of Atomic, the venture studio behind Hims & Hers, Exowatt, and other successful companies.

headline: Seller Ledger Cracks Amazon Accounting Challenges with New Suite of Tools
summary: Launched in March of 2023, Seller Ledger has quickly made a name for itself as an affordable, easy-to-use and highly accurate eCommerce accounting software provider. A stalwart for eBay sellers from its earliest days, the company has significantly expanded its offering for Amazon sellers in recent months.
